<div id="directivos">
  <p>CADU counts with a highly seasoned management team in the Mexican housing development industry, with a proven track during the subprime crises and local housing crisis. The Company relies on its management team as a cornerstone piece of its operational and financial success.</p>
<p>The management team of CADU and its Subsidiaries is comprised of top-level executives (some of them significant shareholders). This management provides great flexibility to the Company, and streamlined the decision-making process to the best interest of the stockholders.</p>
